OL,3,CParents of missing teenager Taylor
OL,4,CCharlton mark his 15th birthday
OL,6,FThe parents of missing Taylor Charlton
OL,7,Ffrom Barnstaple have marked his 15th
OL,8,Fbirthday by thanking the community for
OL,9,Fits "incredible" support.
OL,11,FTaylor was last seen on the night of
OL,12,FFriday 8 May and investigations into
OL,13,Fhis disappearance are continuing.
OL,15,FIn a statement, Taylor's mum and dad,
OL,16,FZoe and Alex, said: "Today is Taylor's
OL,17,F15th birthday.
OL,26,@xD@UOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1779894668
OL,3,CParents of missing teenager Taylor
OL,4,CCharlton mark his 15th birthday
OL,6,F"As Taylor's Mum and Dad, we would
OL,7,Flike to thank everyone locally and
OL,8,Ffurther afield for sharing posts
OL,9,Facross social media in the search for
OL,10,FTaylor.
OL,12,F"The amount of support shown from the
OL,13,Fcommunity has been incredible and
OL,14,Ftruly appreciated by all involved.
OL,16,F"Hundreds of people are continuing to
OL,17,Flook for him, and we cannot thank
OL,18,Feveryone enough for the time, effort
OL,19,Fand support they have given so far.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1779894668
OL,3,CParents of missing teenager Taylor
OL,4,CCharlton mark his 15th birthday
OL,6,F"If anyone would like to get involved
OL,7,Fin the search, please join the
OL,8,FFacebook page and take part in one of
OL,9,Fthe organised local searches."
OL,11,FThey added "Every extra pair of eyes
OL,12,Fcould make a difference. Please
OL,13,Fcontinue sharing posts, staying
OL,14,Fvigilant and supporting the ongoing
OL,15,Fsearch efforts. We just want our son
OL,16,Fhome."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@LOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
