OL,3,CParents of missing teenager Taylor
OL,4,CCharlton mark his 15th birthday
OL,6,FThe last confirmed sighting of Taylor
OL,7,Fwas captured on CCTV in the Tesco
OL,8,FExtra car park, in Station Road, at
OL,9,Faround 10.30pm on Friday 8 May.
OL,10,FFootage shows him heading in the
OL,11,Fdirection of the River Taw.
OL,13,FHe was then reported as missing on
OL,14,FSaturday 9 May at around 5:15pm.
OL,16,FDevon and Cornwall Police say it is
OL,17,Fbelieved that Taylor may have entered
OL,18,Fthe water.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
