FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1779894668
OL,3,CParents of missing teenager Taylor
OL,4,CCharlton mark his 15th birthday
OL,6,FOfficers are carrying out a full
OL,7,Finvestigation of the area including
OL,8,Freviewing CCTV footage and a police
OL,9,Fhelicopter was used to help further
OL,10,Fenquiries along the River Taw and its
OL,11,Festuary over the weekend.
OL,13,FSuperintendent Emma Butler-Jones said:
OL,14,F"Taylor, his family and friends are
OL,15,Fvery much in our thoughts,
OL,16,Fparticularly on his birthday today.
OL,18,F"We remain dedicated to finding
OL,19,Fanswers for Taylor's loved-ones and a
OL,20,Fsubstantial investigation is ongoing.
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
